column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, d.logMass,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, GN.distance, GN.petroR5#_r FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust AS d on d.specObjID = p.objid   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID WHERE  s.z between # and #ORDER BY distance
